<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink101-kilavi">aṟattoṭu niṉṟapiṉṉar varaitaṟporuṭṭup pirinta talaimakaṉ varaivōṭu pukuntavaḻit tōḻi cevilikkuk kāṭṭic colliyatu. 
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">Pointedly said by the confidante to the foster mother, after having stood with righteousness, about the hero who separated for the reason of marriage, [now] entering with a proposal for marriage.</p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink101">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai yutukkā</l>
<l>ṇērkoṭip pācaṭumpu pariyavūr piḻipu</l>
<l>neytaṉ mayakki vantaṉṟu niṉmakaḷ</l>
<l>puppō luṇkaṇ marīiya</l>
<l>nōykkumarun tākiya koṇkaṉ ṟērē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh mother, please mother,  Look there!</l>
<l>The chariot of the sea-man that is the antidote</l>
<l>To the affliction that joins into the flower-like, kajaled eyes of your daughter,</l>
<l>Has come, making the Neytal plant fade, rising and falling,</l>
<l>[And] so that the beautiful creepers of the green Aṭumpu are torn up.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
